WE PUT EASY BAKE IN A BOTTLE 🤭 Meet Easy Bake Setting Spray—your new holy grail for makeup that stays fresh and ultra-blurred for 16 HOURS ⏳

We worked to give you guys this MOST requested product!!!! It was SO hard to bottle that ‘Easy Bake’ flawless matte finish into a setting spray that’s lightweight, breathable, but we did it, AND it’s packed with skin-loving ingredients. 

Why you NEED this in your routine: 🌾 Rice Starch & Mineral Clay keeps shine in control
💧 5 forms of Hyaluronic Acid deeply hydrate + refresh 🔒 Transfer-proof and keeps makeup fresh for 16 HOURS 🚫 Alcohol-free, fragrance-free, and gentle enough for ALL skin types

Lightweight, breathable, and made to melt seamlessly into your skin. Simply SHAKE WELL and spay for fresh, flawless makeup that actually lasts 🤍✨

Get it FIRST at @sephora, March 27. Tap the 🔗 in our bio to join the waitlist now.
